      • GEOHASH_LEVELS

        public static final int GEOHASH_LEVELS
        By default, Lucene's SpatialPrefixTree uses 12 levels which results in sub-meter precision. Our queries are on the scale of kilometers, so we don't need this level of precision - additionally, decreasing the number of levels results in faster queries.
